<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Liege" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Liege,</orth> lord paramount, sovereign: <cit><quote>l. of all loiterers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 3.185" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 185</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my sovereign l. was in my debt,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.129" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 129</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that misbecame my place, my person, or my --'s sovereignty,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.2.101" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 2, 101</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>stirred up my liefest l. to be mine enemy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.164" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 164</bibl></cit>. <emph>Humphrey, proved</emph> (an enemy) <cit><quote>to my l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.164" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 164</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>I tender so the safety of my l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.164" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 164</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>Henry, our dread l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>canst thou speak against thy l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.95" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 95</bibl></cit>. Mostly in the vocative: <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.245" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 245</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.433" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 433</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.214" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 214</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.214" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 214</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.292" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 292</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 34</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 34</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.152" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 152</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.152" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 152</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.234" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 234</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.66" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 170</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.4.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 4, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.94" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.1.86" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 1, 86</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.122" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 4, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 36</bibl> etc. etc.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>